## Guidelines
- Stay at high level - no implementation details
- Focus on "what" and "why", not "how"
- Create clear boundaries between modules
- Design for testability and maintainability
- Consider future evolution and extension points
- Document trade-offs explicitly

## Critical Success Factors
✅ Clear module responsibilities
✅ Minimal and explicit dependencies
✅ Well-defined interfaces
✅ Documented technology choices with alternatives
✅ Identified risks and mitigation strategies

## Completion Criteria
- All 4 documents are complete
- Module boundaries are clear
- Interfaces are defined
- Technology choices are justified
- Ready for Task Decomposition Agent